#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Participant nodes maintain an informatics infrastructure to support the "
#| "publication of biodiversity data by data holders. Many implementation "
#| "models are available, from using hosted data publication services to "
#| "maintaining a distributed network of data publishers and a centralized "
#| "index of the data. The node’s informatics infrastructure may also support "
#| "a range of other information products and services, for example, by "
#| "maintaining a biodiversity data portal and online tools for data analysis."
