msgstr "Gestion et conservation des données sur la biodiversité"

#. type: Plain text
#: 5.-what-do-participant-nodes-need-to-be-effective/5.1-basic-requirements.en.adoc:57
msgid ""
"The ability to manage and curate biodiversity data, as a means of "
"continuously improving data quality."
msgstr ""
"Aptitude à gérer et à conserver les données sur la biodiversité afin "
"d’améliorer continuellement la qualité des données."

#. type: Plain text
#: 5.-what-do-participant-nodes-need-to-be-effective/5.1-basic-requirements.en.adoc:60
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "A workflow for contributing to data quality improvement, linked to the "
#| "processes of endorsing data publishers joining the GBIF network and "
