#: 5.-what-do-participant-nodes-need-to-be-effective/5.1-basic-requirements.en.adoc:65
msgid "The ability to access, analyze and use biodiversity data."
msgstr ""
"Aptitude à accéder, analyser et utiliser les données sur la biodiversité."

#. type: Plain text
#: 5.-what-do-participant-nodes-need-to-be-effective/5.1-basic-requirements.en.adoc:68
