#| "level through a survey, workshop or literature analysis (possibly led by "
#| "a consultant) can provide valuable information to guide the stakeholder "
#| "group in formulating their recommendations. This assessment helps ensure "
#| "that the needs and priorities of a broad stakeholder group are "
#| "represented in the process. Tools for stakeholder mapping (as in example "
#| "tools 4 to 6 http://www.fao.org/fileadmin/user_upload/capacity_building/"
#| "LM4_v2_WEB_Light.pdf[here]) can also shape an understanding how the "
